And heres to notation for adding the coords

The first thing is go to the North West corner of your safezone. do ::mypos and the coords that come up, add the to the “x” not the “y”
Now go to southwest corner and do ::mypos again. Those 2 numbers, add them to the first and last “y”.

Then save and compile, and you have your safezone
